{{Quote|Lowbacca was the only one who completely understood the biomechanics of the ''Maledoth''. So as you can see, the Ramoan relocation project has ground to a complete standstill.|[[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]]|<ref name="Dark Nest I: The Joiner King">''[[Dark Nest I: The Joiner King]]''</ref>}}
The '''Ramoan relocation project''' was a project headed by the [[New Jedi Order]] to use a former [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[slaveship]], the ''[[Maledoth]]'', in order to relocate [[Ramoan|the population]] of a [[Ramoa|dying]] [[Planet/Legends|world]] to a more suitable place. The project came to a standstill when [[Lowbacca]] left to answer a call to the [[Unknown Regions/Legends|Unknown Regions]] from [[Raynar Thul]].

